QUICK INSTALL for Linux

	As root or user type:

		./configure
		make

	To check the generated executable type:

		make check

	and as root to install the programs and the documentation
	type:

		make install

	then change the example configuration file advscan.rc to
	your requirements.

	The documentation is in the advscan, advzip and advdiff
	manpages accessible with the commands:

		man advscan
		man advzip
		man advdiff


QUICK INSTALL for DOS

	Download the binary version and copy the executables on
	your path.

	The documentation is in the advscan.txt, advzip.txt and
	advdiff.txt files.

